  body
    .container-fluid
      .row.intro
        .col-md-6.col-sm-8.intro-left
          .intro-left-content
            p
              img(src='https://www.printyourbrackets.com/ncaa-logos/boston-college-eagles-logo.png', width='600', height='350', alt='Template Logo')
            h1 Test-X.
            p.lead A test creator designed to work with CameraMouse - a BC initiative.
            p
              | Enter your username to create a new test for your student!
            form(action="/views/main", method="post")
              span.form-group
                label(for='username')
                input#username.form-inline(type='username', name = 'username', placeholder='Enter Username')
              button.btn.btn-default.btn-sm(type='submit') Submit
